                        <p>1776. For <persName corresp="#p_JUA_1">Johnson</persName>.</p>
                        <p>Following is text Tokyo’s 2237:</p>
                        <p>(Code Rm. please repeat Tokyo’s 2237, Control 12066 and 12065)</p>
                        <closer>
